{"tid":1669874,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"解決加泰集會問題嘅方法","createTime":"2019-10-22T21:16:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T04:47:04.000Z","uid":321542,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"af0b8f379a90da2889b962b41391dba7051c3fdc","tid":1669874,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:16:44.000Z","msg":"既然阻止唔到加泰集會<br />\n主辦方又拒絕將集會改為聲援全球人權民主集會<br />\n咁以下嘅方法希望可以解決呢個集會帶來的問題<br />\n<br />\n利申: 支持加泰,但反對加泰集會<br />\nbtw先唔講方法,講點解我支持加泰但反對呢次集會<br />\n<br />\n1, 智利,印尼,黎巴嫩都搞緊野,點解只係搞支持加泰only<br />\n2,印尼有女記者係香港中彈,係搞都係先支持印尼啦<br />\n3,呢幾日口交部,美國同Solomon Yue嘅口風,冇留意嘅連登大把文講緊<br />\n4,明明全球集會都可以包埋加泰,點解佢地死都唔改?<br />\n<br />\n唔係要同佢地割,但係個集會真係唔係太合理<br />\n所以,以下有3個方案希望可以解決加泰集會問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1, 騎劫左佢做聲援全球人權民主集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處: 直接解決問題<br />\n壞處: 容易俾對家抹黑(將騎劫集會嘅人數計入加泰集會),需要文宣講解騎劫左集會同騎劫嘅原因<br />\n<br />\n2, 無視佢,等個集會冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處: 可以同加泰切割<br />\n壞處: 容易俾人話加泰人以香港為榜樣結果香港人連聲都唔敢出,破壞形象,同埋有割蓆feel<br />\n<br />\n3, 同日同時唔同地搞多個聲援全球人權民主集會<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好處: 避免破壞香港人支持人權民主形象之餘又唔會咁易俾人抹黑<br />\n壞處: 分散人數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然問題來到,我地要做嘅應該係用腦解決問題而唔係諗篤灰/話人係鬼<br />\n<br />\n記住,核彈都唔割<br />\n<br />\n但不完美嘅就要改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家幫手諗下點改善加泰集會呢個不完美<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63820639f1726d8b2baea1e023c30cc1c624b54","tid":1669874,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:18:17.000Z","msg":"p仔自推 1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4070b4b8b4ac04ffc630e3228e1c82bd4217dd","tid":1669874,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:18:42.000Z","msg":"p仔推唔郁 2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83adbf1f6a7e092519d788f48aed98aeebe506c2","tid":1669874,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:19:09.000Z","msg":"p仔推車 3/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0868c52d769bd3c37f21480cda38d68bb58a929","tid":1669874,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:20:37.000Z","msg":"dllm p仔冇人權 4/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f12bf746313d0309018173688a19a727f3dc8bc1","tid":1669874,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:21:19.000Z","msg":"p仔後悔唔早d入連登 5/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23aa596a1271c6c3dd3c4ba73b227158ebbd5c32","tid":1669874,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:23:33.000Z","msg":"p仔諗唔到點作落去 6/6 就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5ed2cbd90639bced1bc83ba68a414324392a0d","tid":1669874,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:25:40.000Z","msg":"p仔玩下你啫 點都推夠10次 7/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9637e69dc642bc43e79bada18537467a34d43aec","tid":1669874,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:28:56.000Z","msg":"p仔話幫手推下 p仔推唔郁 8/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7011375aef50517e4be871e542e4705334a0126","tid":1669874,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T21:30:03.000Z","msg":"p仔話早知標題改吸引d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"271e291140fc5a0c4ddf879509aebc8d8c350bce","tid":1669874,"uid":321542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7011375aef50517e4be871e542e4705334a0126","tid":1669874,"uid":321542,"like":